<dec f='include/SDL/SDL_mutex.h' l='166' type='int SDL_CondWaitTimeout(SDL_cond * cond, SDL_mutex * mutex, Uint32 ms)'/>
<doc f='include/SDL/SDL_mutex.h' l='160'>/** Waits for at most &apos;ms&apos; milliseconds, and returns 0 if the condition
 *  variable is signaled, SDL_MUTEX_TIMEDOUT if the condition is not
 *  signaled in the allotted time, and -1 on error.
 *  On some platforms this function is implemented by looping with a delay
 *  of 1 ms, and so should be avoided if possible.
 */</doc>
